phantom-wan-mlx
Apple MLX port of Phantom-Wan (ByteDance, https://github.com/Phantom-video/Phantom).

Derived from:
- Phantom-video/Phantom — Apache-2.0 (code + weights, bytedance-research/Phantom)
- Wan2.1 (Wan-AI) — VAE / umT5 / scheduler substrate
- mlx-video (Blaizzy) — Wan MLX backbone reused via the LongCat-Video port

